Package etomica.molecule.iterator

Class MoleculeIteratorAllMolecules

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.molecule.iterator.MoleculeIteratorArrayListSimple
      • etomica.molecule.iterator.MoleculeIteratorAllMolecules
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AtomsetIterator, MoleculeIterator, MoleculeIteratorBoxDependent, MoleculesetIterator, MoleculesetIteratorBoxDependent

    public class MoleculeIteratorAllMolecules
extends MoleculeIteratorArrayListSimple
implements MoleculeIteratorBoxDependent
    Iterator for all the molecules in a box. Loops over all those atoms that lie just below the species agents in the atom tree hierarchy. To iterate the molecules of just one species, use AtomIteratorMolecule.
    Since:
    02.02.16
